msgid "Abjad Widget - Local Dashboard"
msgstr "Abjad Widget - Dashboard y'ahantu"

msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Abashakishije Umwuka n'Abanyamwuka"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Inyota, introspective, ifite umutwe mwiza, no "
"gushishikazwa n'ubumenyi bw'ibanga. Bashobora kugira inyungu ikomeye mu "
"kugaragaza ibisobanuro by'ibanga cyangwa imiterere mu buzima. Imirimo: "
"Abarimu b'umwuka, abasomyi ba tarot, abashakashatsi ku nyenyeri, cyangwa "
"abantu bakora mu bikorwa bya New Age. Imiterere y'Inyungu: Bashobora kuba "
"bafite imyemerere y'umwuka cyangwa y'ibimenyetso. Bashobora kubona "
"ibikoresho nk'uburyo bwo guhuza n'ukuri kwimbitse cyangwa imbaraga z'isi."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Abakunzi ba Gematria n'imibare"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Inyurabwenge, ifite umwihariko w'ibikurikiranwa, "
"yishimira kumenya imibanire hagati y'imibare n'ururimi. Bashobora kwishimira"
" kwiga ibijyanye n'ibimenyetso. Imirimo: Abakora mu mibare, abanditsi "
"b'amakuru ku bintu by'ibanga, cyangwa abashaka kwiga imibare. Imiterere "
"y'Inyungu: Bashobora kuva ku bantu bareba imibare nk'ibikorwa by'ubwenge "
"byoroshye kugeza ku bantu bizeyeko ifite agaciro k'umwuka kenshi."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Abashakashatsi mu mateka n'ururimi"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Ubufatanye, butumire, n'icyifuzo cyo kumenya "
"amateka cyangwa imico y'ibikoresho by'imibare nka Abjad. Imirimo: "
"Abanyamuryango, abashakashatsi, cyangwa abanyeshuri basoma indimi z'ibiyaga "
"by'Iburasirazuba, amateka, cyangwa inyandiko z'iyobokamana. Imiterere "
"y'Inyungu: Bashobora gufata ibikoresho mu buryo bw'ubukungu, bw'uburezi, "
"bigendeye ku mateka cyangwa imico y'ubumenyi bw'ukuri."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Abantu b'Imana cyangwa Abayoboke"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Umuvugizi, wifuza gufata umwanya wo gutekereza, no "
"gushaka umubano wimbitse w'ukuri. Bashobora gukoresha ibikoresho ngo basome "
"inyandiko z'iyobokamana cyangwa ubutumwa bwo mu ruhando. Imirimo: "
"Abanyamuryango b'iyobokamana, imams, abayoboke, cyangwa abantu bafite "
"inyungu ikomeye mu ndangagaciro z'ubuzima bw'iyobokamana. Imiterere "
"y'Inyungu: Bashobora kugira ishusho isanzwe cyangwa ishingiye ku muco, "
"bakoresha ibikoresho ngo bugarure imyemerere y'ukuri."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Abanditsi n'Abahanzi"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Gukora, kwiyumvamo, no gushishikazwa n'ibitekerezo "
"by'imbonerahamwe cyangwa ibitekerezo by'ibanze. Bashobora gukoresha "
"ibikoresho ngo bibukirwe cyangwa kongeraho ibice by'inyongera mu kazi kabo. "
"Imirimo: Abanyanditsi, abahanzi, abahanga mu ishusho, cyangwa abahanzi. "
"Imiterere y'Inyungu: Bashobora kuva ku bakora mu buryo bw'ubukungu kugeza ku"
" bantu bafite inyungu mu by'ukuri cyangwa mu by'ibanga."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Abakunzi b'imikino y'ibibazo n'ibibazo"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Gukina, n'ubushakashatsi bw'ubwenge, no kwishimira "
"gukemura ibibazo by'ubwiyongere cyangwa gusobanura imiterere. Imirimo: "
"Abanyamuryango, abashakashatsi mu mikino, cyangwa abarimu. Imiterere "
"y'Inyungu: Bashobora gufata ibikoresho nk'uburyo bwo gukina cyangwa imyitozo"
" y'ubwonko, nta nkomoko y'ibitekerezo."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr ""
"Abashakashatsi ku mikorere y'inkiko n'abakora ibitekerezo by'inyurabwenge"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Imiterere y'ibitekerezo: Igitekerezo cy'ibibazo by'ikinyoma, no "
"gushishikazwa no kubona ukuri kw'ibanga cyangwa imiterere mu mirimo. "
"Imirimo: Abashakashatsi b'ubwisanzure, abashushanya, cyangwa abashishikazwa."
" Imiterere y'Inyungu: Bashobora kugira ishusho ikomeye cyangwa itandukanye, "
"bakoresha ibikoresho ngo bifashe mu gushyigikira ibitekerezo cyangwa inkuru "
"zitandukanye."

